      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $f : \\R \\to \\R$ une fonction de classe $\\mathcal{C}^2$.\nOn suppose : $\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f(x)| \\le \\alpha$ et $|f''(x)| \\le \\beta$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f : \\R \\to \\R\\)</span> une fonction de classe <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}^2\\)</span>. On suppose : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f(x)| \\le \\alpha\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(|f&#39;&#39;(x)| \\le \\beta\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "455b1a3a-73ee-4915-abb1-4d2dc3df0685",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que : $\\forall\\ h > 0,\\ \\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f'(x)| \\le \\frac {2\\alpha}h + \\frac {h\\beta}2$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ h &gt; 0,\\ \\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f&#39;(x)| \\le \\frac {2\\alpha}h + \\frac {h\\beta}2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5246cab2-aec0-41db-b10d-5d6f2ec39797",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$f(x+h) = f(x) + hf'(x) + \\frac {h^2}2f''(x+\\theta h)  \\Rightarrow \n     f'(x) = \\frac {f(x+h) - f(x)}h -\\frac h2f''(x+\\theta h)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x+h) = f(x) + hf&#39;(x) + \\frac {h^2}2f&#39;&#39;(x+\\theta h)  \\Rightarrow \n     f&#39;(x) = \\frac {f(x+h) - f(x)}h -\\frac h2f&#39;&#39;(x+\\theta h)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ae051aa3-e804-4e8d-b776-153b2d96920a",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour quelle valeur de $h$ obtient-on la meilleure inégalité ?",
        "html": "<p>Pour quelle valeur de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(h\\)</span> obtient-on la meilleure inégalité ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7547b058-f56d-4347-a033-02aad070c4de",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$h = 2\\sqrt{\\alpha/\\beta}  \\Rightarrow  |f'| \\le 2\\sqrt{\\alpha\\beta}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(h = 2\\sqrt{\\alpha/\\beta}  \\Rightarrow  |f&#39;| \\le 2\\sqrt{\\alpha\\beta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
